The paper proposes a model for embedding multi-relational graph data in hyperbolic space, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and databases (cs.DB). The model is evaluated on a knowledge graph, which is a type of structured data often used in natural language processing (cs.CL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper discusses the performance of the model at lower dimensionality, which is a common concern in the field of scalable and efficient algorithms (cs.SI).
